Package it.polimi.ingsw.core.model

Class Card

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.core.model.CardGame
it.polimi.ingsw.core.model.Card
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
GoldCard, Objective, ResourceCard
public abstract class Card extends CardGame implements Serializable
This abstract class represents a card in the game. It extends CardGame and implements Serializable interface. It maintains the front and back corners, back resources, centre, and matrix coordinates of the card.
